   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="Arthur-Schnitzler_an_Hermann-Bahr_00232"/>Herrn</addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Hermann Bahr</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb165" type="place">Wien Ober St. Veit</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb220" type="place">Veitli<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>enga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="Arthur-Schnitzler_an_Hermann-Bahr_00233"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb298283"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Wien, XVIII, Sternwartestr. 71</rs>.</hi></rs></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="Arthur-Schnitzler_an_Hermann-Bahr_00232"/><salute>herzlichen Dank, lieber Hermann</salute> für dein neues <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02090-1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb30035" subtype="implied">B<damage agent="hole"><supplied>uc</supplied></damage>h</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02090-1"><bibl><rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person">Hermann Bahr</rs>: <rs ref="#pmb30035" type="work">Inventur</rs>. Berlin: <rs ref="#pmb29639" type="org">S. Fischer</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>1912</date></bibl>.</note> u viele Grüße. Ob die dich <damage agent="hole"><supplied>tre</supplied></damage>ffen werden, wei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s ich nicht – de<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> niemand
               wei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02090-2"/>wo du bi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02090-2"><rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person">Bahr</rs> war zumindest seit <date>Mitte
                     September</date> mehrere Wochen in der <rs ref="#pmb144" type="place">Villa
                        Mautner</rs>.</note>. So<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ei denn der Findigkeit der Po<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <pb facs="Arthur-Schnitzler_an_Hermann-Bahr_00233"/>vertraut. Au<damage agent="hole"><supplied>f</supplied></damage> bald!</p><closer>Dein <signed>Arthur</signed></closer><postscript><dateline><date><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02090-3"/>26/9 1912<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02090-3">Der Poststempel widerspricht der
                        Datierung.</note></date></dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
